item.title: CVE-2021-20833|2024-08-03T17:53:22.674Z -- soda%2C%20inc. -- snkrdunk%20market%20place%20app%20for%20ios
item.description: The SNKRDUNK Market Place App for iOS versions prior to 2.2.0 does not verify server certificate properly, which allows man-in-the-middle attackers to eavesdrop on and/or alter encrypted communication via a crafted certificate.
